All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
BackTestResult
A backtest result wrapper containing the strategy positions and its statistics.
BackTestService
Service to backtest a TradingStrategy
BarSeriesService
A service for manipulating BarSeries
BarService
A service for manipulating Bars.
PositionService
A service to get the position of a TradingStrategy over a BarSeries or a CandlestickInterval
StrategyBuilder
Service to build a ta4j strategy over a TradingStrategy.
StrategyCallback
Strategy and stream handler.
SymbolBar
A Bar with the name of its symbol.
TradingStatistics
Statistics results of a trading backtest.
TradingStrategy
A trading strategy with an entry and an exit Rules based on technical indicators, able to analyse, backtest or live test a BarSeries / Candle
WatchService
Service to live trade a TradingStrategy.
